Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:47.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,THE CLIENT FULL OF LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:47.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I really must see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm a little tied up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything that can be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm actually near your office already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's OK, I'd like to at least talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lightning has come flying through!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The winner is Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that amazing come-from-behind\Nvictory, the final race is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just say I was busy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean, discussing it would be just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do your work already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what kind of person called just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was some older woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she's coming over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll be like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Please help me find my long lost first love!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll definitely be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ikenami, who just called a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for intruding on you so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:20.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ikenami Shizuka\NClient
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:21.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My friend claimed that if I asked Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nfor help, we could find him easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I very much so hope you'll help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, come sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's such a beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did Dad go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies for having you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madamosielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was busy reviewing some elementary murder case files.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, please have a seat on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we may rest your heart before discussing this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's begun again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're looking for a classmate from middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were both involved in kendo as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't there be an address in the yearbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he moved before graduation, the\Ninformation supplied for him was minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a photograph from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for the one in the center holding the gold cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Shibata Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this cute girl next to him be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This photograph is already thirty years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thirty years old!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you're over forty years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I turn forty-two this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since this photograph was taken\Nwhen he was in the seventh grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably a bit taller now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I get a list of hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, he likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really liked knitting, so I make a lot of sweaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a perfect hobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother likes to knit as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're probably a great cook as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not good at it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ended up doing this while trying last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Women with weaknesses are more attractive anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I really have a lot of weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably why I'm still single at this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're single!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe men haven't noticed\Nsuch a beautiful and honorable woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must all be blind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like the person who split from\Nmy mother, what were they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, my throat just isn't well right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm allergic to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just cleaning, so there's dust everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we can go elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you want to find this\NShibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is to ask for that photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The photograph was taken when we were\Nin eighth grade, on the summer fair day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a picture of me holding\Nthe championship plaque.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandmother accidentally threw\Nthe award away a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I thought about it and was reminded of that photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why does Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} have the photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was using it as a bookmark while reading a\Nbook I borrowed from him and forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I realized it, he was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't want to find him because he's your first love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any other information?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iced lemon tea for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Reiko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just what he used to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used to say there was a character named Reiko in the\Nbook he let me borrow that had a personality like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what will you have, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iced coffee for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This definitely isn't enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With only his name, age, and a thirty\Nyear old photograph to go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should have used that person's brilliant mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard others mention him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That high school detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say Kudou Shinichi comes and\Ngoes from your detective agency often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, that brat won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only gives us a stupid call every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know they were so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if this was noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By them already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could they have already deduced this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you about to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the point in asking this brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But sometimes he notices interesting\Nthings that no one else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this guy is holding the cup,\Nhe must have got first place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was already this good in seventh grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have attended some sort of recorded\Ncompetition at some point, even if he had problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a person who participated named Shibata Shirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say he always participates and is usually in the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's a physical education\Nteacher at Shizouka High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lives together with his wife at an apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go call for a rent-a-car now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great that we've found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've already found who she was looking for, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What confuses me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This woman full of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She lied about everything she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiding her identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, or could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this woman be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess no one's in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's Sunday, they may have gone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's head out and come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:18.03,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa Takezou (47)\NFriend of Shibata Shirou
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's coming over to my place to play mah-jong later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it doesn't seem like he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must just be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, the door's unlocked, TV's on, and he's asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're about to get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, he only ate half of his food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The soup is already cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So is the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this have been breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a waste of fresh guji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's west lake fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:28.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Shibata Kyouko (38)\NWife of Shibata Shirou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You think you can just go into anyone's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm calling the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something in his right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now let's review your statements...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you four came to visit Shibata Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nand after ringing the doorbell a number of times...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one answered?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came to meet Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nand found the door wasn't locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you entered with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lastly, there's his wife, Kyouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who\Nmet with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} moments before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} found Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body in the living room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dead, with his head covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is some time in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where was his wife at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I arranged to meet some friends for golf,\Nwho came around 5:00 A.M in their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had prepared him breakfast and left before 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, at that time, Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he came home around 3:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you just say 3:00 A.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's mah-jong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were playing mah-jong in my room down on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As she said, we quit around 3:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, there's that newspaper next to his breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know when it was delivered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's always delivered to the mailbox at around 6:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got up, collected the newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, while he was enjoying his breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was attacked and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the most likely scenario, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What tells you he was eating breakfast then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because some of the food on the\Ntable was eaten, and then it went cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, who is responsible for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who killed my husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're still not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, when you entered...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The TV was on that whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The TV was!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was it off when we arrived!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a little noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he was just watching TV and eating breakfast, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was most likely watching that show, "The Hero\NSword Legend," which airs every morning at 8:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:16:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He records it every week and watches it in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There definitely are a lot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check the TV recorder in the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why isn't the LD player here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are LD discs over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no player.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't this spot particularly empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one speaker, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be being repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, actually, my husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with this case, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with your questioning so I can get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I'll need to confirm it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you get the contact information\Nfor those you were golfing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That goes for you and your mah-jong friends as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They actually picked up the wife at 5:00 A.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, according to her friends, the time\Nwas reported on the car's radio then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time they brought her home,\Nit was already past 7:00 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,7:00 P.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we come after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to the newspaper publisher, and they\Nsaid the papers are delivered at 6:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the TV show was recorded, I estimate\Nthat the time of death would probably be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around forty-five minutes prior to 8:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that means the wife couldn't have committed the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I must ask Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're behaving very strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have an alibi for 8:00 A.M. this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I was asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anyone see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember leaving a message after calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, "It's time to wake up, I'm coming up now."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I killed him, would I have left that message?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have done it so we wouldn't suspect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you questioning them, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way he's the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is someone I can respect: Detective Mouri Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's his daughter, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and the\Nkid who lives with them, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, that beauty beside him is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to help find an old acquaintance\Nof mine, who happened to be Shibata Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Ikenami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only came to get a thirty year-old\Nphotograph back from Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be the photo in his hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just saw it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The photograph I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why would Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} be holding this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This photograph is Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s dying message, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be connected to the beautiful Shizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, the photograph should be in an album.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have fallen out or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something under that man's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Thunder God's Door{\i0} is the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The book you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that would be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I borrowed it from Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} thirty years ago and\Nleft my photograph inside when I returned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could the criminal be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that an overwhelming coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like how the book and photograph are both on the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was that strange phone call yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, from Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said, "This is interesting, you should come see."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have been watching a video in this living room then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was talking with someone on the\Nphone while looking for a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he turned to a certain page of one of\Nthem and said, smiling, "I got it, I got it."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did your husband put that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on top of that stack of books in front of the bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found blood in the corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the murder started in this corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. CSI Guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I see that book for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is important evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, this is a ninja book with a lot of kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A boy like you can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you've read the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, is there a character named "Reiko" in the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no character by that name in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's another lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This woman is a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, for what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just why is she lying like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:26.86,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,THE CLIENT FULL OF LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:26.86,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found a bloody bokken!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was behind the stairs near the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, did your husband keep a bokken here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:43.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:46.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Shibata Kyouko (38)\NWife of Shibata Shirou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's kept on that counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:49.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My husband used it to chase away salesmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how many phones do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one in the bedroom and one in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We used to have one near the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal is Ikenami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.91,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ikenami Shizuka (42)\NClient
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:11.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You are the one responsible for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Detective Yokomizo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You first called to confirm that the\Nphotograph was indeed still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came yourself to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then had an argument with him\Nover the photograph near the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which ended with you taking the\Nbokken in hand and attacking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You escaped via the rear stairs after\Nyou thought you had killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was still holding on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He fought his way to the living room to get to the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, just before him, was the photo\Nof you inside of {\i1}The Thunder God's Door{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.07,0:23:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With his last bit of life, Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} reached for the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then had a photograph of his killer in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be something secret in the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why she asked you to help her find the photograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Ikenami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you come with us to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't be coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want a statement from me, won't you need\Nto get an arrest warrant from the courts first?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.95,0:24:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, based on so little evidence, you\Nwon't be able to prove I'm involved at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, you will have some difficulty\Narresting me without a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.38,0:24:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, the wife could decide to\Npress charges against us for trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.72,0:25:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.85,0:25:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.15,0:25:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.56,0:25:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's blood here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.94,0:25:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have just reached for his injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.61,0:25:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.53,0:25:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bandages on his fingers have no blood on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.78,0:25:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.74,0:25:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman's left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.41,0:25:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.37,0:25:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.67,0:25:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.05,0:25:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.30,0:25:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.01,0:25:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.05,0:25:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.05,0:25:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, the criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.43,0:25:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person came...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.23,0:25:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before we did...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.40,0:25:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To this blood-stained murder scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.07,0:25:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, come on, Ikenami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.82,0:25:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim, Shibata Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was holding\Na photograph of you, was he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.87,0:26:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of relationship would you have with him\Nthat had him holding a photograph of you as he died?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.54,0:26:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already explained this to Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.34,0:26:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, please come repeat it at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.63,0:26:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.39,0:26:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be holding you responsible for my\Npredicament, Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.27,0:26:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I am a client of yours who is\Nrecording a statement with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.40,0:26:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.82,0:26:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.36,0:26:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you already get my statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.03,0:26:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there should be no need...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.16,0:26:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.46,0:26:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.29,0:26:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.71,0:26:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.34,0:26:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.09,0:26:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.68,0:27:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ikenami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.97,0:27:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With things as they are, you cannot\Navoid being questioned, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.60,0:27:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.68,0:27:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.06,0:27:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not as a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.98,0:27:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will now show the truth of the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.44,0:27:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With her as my key witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.24,0:27:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, she really didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.45,0:27:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.70,0:27:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She came here with us for the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.75,0:27:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we came here together earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.04,0:27:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We rang the door bell a number of times to no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.09,0:27:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She could have opened the door herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.22,0:27:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she had been the one that killed Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.48,0:27:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would have known the door was already unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.32,0:28:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't have missed her chance to retrieve the\Nphotograph before the police arrived either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.07,0:28:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's the one who opened the door immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.87,0:28:12.71,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa Takezou (47)\NFriend of Shibata Shirou
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.87,0:28:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.12,0:28:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.83,0:28:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's not forget that you were also the first to find the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.17,0:28:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to get here before the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.80,0:28:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get rid of the evidence, isn't that right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.93,0:28:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.97,0:28:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} isn't the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.48,0:28:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Shibata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was dead before at least noon...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.85,0:28:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can assume the door was already open.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.90,0:28:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, from the estimated time of death, Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nhad no alibi and couldn't risk returning to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.66,0:28:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that he didn't know\Nthere was evidence to remove.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.00,0:28:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why would he come back to the murder half a day later?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.59,0:29:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why would he call when he\Nknows only a corpse could answer it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.59,0:29:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we arrived, he shouted at us and told us not to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.48,0:29:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were the culprit, I'd wait until I was alone to go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.52,0:29:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.52,0:29:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could the culprit be...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.86,0:29:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.07,0:29:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one with the best alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.12,0:29:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.08,0:29:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.41,0:29:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could the culprit be...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.63,0:29:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.63,0:29:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one with the best alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.76,0:29:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.30,0:29:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibata Kyouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.18,0:29:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}wife{\i0} is the culprit!?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.97,0:29:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, did you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.93,0:29:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.35,0:30:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't she leave after preparing breakfast at 5:00 A.M.?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.69,0:30:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could the morning newspaper that\Narrived at 6:00 A.M. be on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.45,0:30:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it wasn't until after 7:00 P.M.\Nthat her friends brought her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.66,0:30:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when you arrived, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.87,0:30:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you came before her...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.29,0:30:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did she get the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.42,0:30:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In actuality, it's all due to her using her time very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.81,0:30:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both 7:05 and 7:10 are "after 7:00."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.10,0:30:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could she have not returned home before we arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.65,0:30:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.78,0:30:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.87,0:30:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's more likely a meal Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had at 3:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.20,0:31:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if you put the morning newspaper next to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.46,0:31:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like breakfast, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.46,0:31:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what about the video?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.55,0:31:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't his program recorded at 8:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.64,0:31:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.10,0:31:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just set the timer and the video tape will record automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.64,0:31:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means she had to just make the arrangements...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.27,0:31:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you waited for your husband to return\Nhome at 3:00 A.M. and have a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.86,0:31:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you had to leave at 5:00 A.M.,\Nyou prepared a late night meal for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.87,0:31:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, while he was eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.21,0:31:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called him out to the corridor and hit him with the bokken.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.63,0:31:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, you set the video timer...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.96,0:31:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Locked the door from outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.22,0:31:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And waited for your friends to arrive\Nat the apartment building at 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.68,0:32:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you arrived home at 7:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.06,0:32:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took the newspaper from the door\Npostbox and put it by the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.61,0:32:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, after you called the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.69,0:32:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You would have a perfect alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.07,0:32:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.45,0:32:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the coroner came and saw the newspaper and video...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.37,0:32:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would be led to believe the victim had breakfast\Naround 8:00 A.M., and had been killed around that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.71,0:32:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, something that wasn't in her plan came up...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.21,0:32:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because her husband wasn't in\Nthe corridor where she'd left him...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.55,0:32:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had struggled into the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.97,0:32:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.43,0:32:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.52,0:32:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, still in shock from seeing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.77,0:32:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phone rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.31,0:32:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could the caller then have been me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.86,0:32:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.86,0:32:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s message saying, "I'm coming up now."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.45,0:32:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hearing this message, she realized immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.74,0:33:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That it would be far better for her if someone\Nelse found the body and then called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.00,0:33:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was then that she decided to leave\Nand pretend to come back shortly after.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.93,0:33:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, where was she before?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.68,0:33:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was likely waiting behind the main door on the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.19,0:33:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.31,0:33:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we showed up before Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.78,0:33:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.61,0:33:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with that photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.99,0:33:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was he holding a photograph of that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.66,0:33:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nothing more than camouflage used to cover up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.21,0:33:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Camouflage?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.04,0:33:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at the victim's left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.88,0:33:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though there's blood on his palm...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.38,0:33:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's none on the bandage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.64,0:34:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.35,0:34:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, look at his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.73,0:34:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.36,0:34:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.52,0:34:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.03,0:34:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before she found him in the living\Nroom, he was clenching it tightly...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.95,0:34:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The proof of their marriage: his wedding ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.33,0:34:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always wore the ring on his left\Nhand's fourth finger, but the wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.17,0:34:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She noticed he wasn't wearing it but holding\Nit in his right hand, so she removed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.60,0:34:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it's unnatural for a hand to\Nbe clenched so tightly around nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.02,0:34:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when she decided to put the picture of\NIkenami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from the nearby book in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.11,0:34:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.36,0:35:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's to ensure the evidence leads to anyone except her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.07,0:35:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.99,0:35:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, she noticed the traces of a ring being on his ring finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.08,0:35:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is why she covered it with a bandage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.97,0:35:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's less obvious if the other\Nfingers have bandages on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.68,0:35:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo, it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.26,0:35:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are traces of a ring being under the bandage!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.48,0:35:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a photograph now!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.14,0:35:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.81,0:35:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next up is the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.02,0:35:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search everywhere in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.06,0:35:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.03,0:35:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.70,0:35:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likely still has it in her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.78,0:35:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you wiped the blood off of the\Nring, there's still chemical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.25,0:35:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she was afraid the police would\Nfind it, she couldn't hide it in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.17,0:35:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, she couldn't leave it on the rear stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.84,0:36:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The best plan is to take it as far away\Nas possible once the police have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.13,0:36:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I believe she still has it on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.76,0:36:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her husband held it tightly as he slowly faded away...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.18,0:36:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His dying message that proved his wife killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.99,0:36:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess good endings really don't exist for bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.95,0:36:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What he and Yoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did going unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.87,0:36:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.63,0:36:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gambling on mah-jong!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.59,0:36:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was gambling day and night on mah-jong!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.51,0:36:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The more he gambled, the more he got into debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.26,0:36:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sold the computer, my jewelry, the car,\Nthe LD player, the speaker system...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.39,0:36:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All until we had nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.60,0:36:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate that damn game!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.02,0:36:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, my husband said...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.90,0:36:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My golf clubs were next.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.11,0:37:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said my father's dowry was after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.11,0:37:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband left me with no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.86,0:37:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we'll need you to come to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.99,0:37:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just let me get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.38,0:37:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dowry...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.30,0:37:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Katana!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.46,0:37:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could she...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.01,0:37:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.60,0:37:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all the only choice I had!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.89,0:37:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the only way to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.27,0:37:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.44,0:37:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.11,0:37:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I killed someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.57,0:37:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.73,0:37:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.25,0:37:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.50,0:37:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.13,0:38:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just tell you to stay away!?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.30,0:38:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you want to take another life?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.39,0:38:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After already killing your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.73,0:38:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you want to kill again?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.89,0:38:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another life?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.81,0:38:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to take my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.61,0:38:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.48,0:38:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Life is the most precious of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.69,0:38:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you give in so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.95,0:38:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such behavior makes you no different\Nthan cold-blooded murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.99,0:38:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Learn to appreciate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.00,0:38:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.71,0:38:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.21,0:38:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.46,0:38:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.76,0:38:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One last thing, Ikenami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.93,0:38:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind revealing them to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.18,0:38:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The meanings behind those four lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.35,0:39:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You claimed you were allergic to dust, but enjoyed knitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.61,0:39:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you didn't like cooking, but you\Nrecognized the type of fish on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.32,0:39:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're also married.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.66,0:39:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a bandage on your left hand's fourth finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.70,0:39:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And "Reiko"...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.87,0:39:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no such character in that ninja book.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.29,0:39:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just said it casually at the coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.80,0:39:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was "Reiko" really?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.68,0:39:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Reiko" was actually "Reikoo."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.30,0:39:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were probably going to ask for iced coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.93,0:39:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you stopped abruptly when you realized asking for iced\Ncoffee by saying "reikoo" would reveal you were from Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.90,0:39:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's something only old men and women say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.65,0:39:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.90,0:39:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.57,0:39:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.62,0:39:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.49,0:40:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, old lady, isn't it time to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.21,0:40:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.58,0:40:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.42,0:40:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you be so rude and call Shizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} an "old lady"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.09,0:40:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really doubt she'd mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.96,0:40:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.85,0:40:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be lying, since...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.60,0:40:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have different skin tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.44,0:40:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.44,0:40:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I inherited my dark skin from my grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.52,0:40:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.57,0:40:32.57,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by Kuraki Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.57,0:40:32.57,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Start in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.82,0:40:39.37,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,ii koto bakari no mirai ja nai keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.82,0:40:39.37,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Even though the future won't just have good things
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.16,0:40:54.89,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,tashika ni ima wa ashita ni mukai dare yori mo kagayaki
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.16,0:40:54.89,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,For now I'm definitely going to face tomorrow shining brighter than anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.84,0:41:11.61,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,koko ni tatteiru koware kake souna ima ni namidashi soredemo
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.84,0:41:11.61,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Because I'm standing here crying for a present that seems about to fall apart, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.86,0:41:17.70,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,We can start in my life issho ni
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.86,0:41:17.70,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,We can start in my life, together
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.99,0:41:22.04,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,akiramezu yume to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.99,0:41:22.04,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,With a dream that we'll never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.96,0:41:34.09,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,nee mou hitori no jibun ni aeru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.96,0:41:34.09,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,You know, it's because you can meet another part of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.59,0:41:41.56,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,kimochi hitotsu de kawarerun da
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.59,0:41:41.56,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,That we can be transformed by a single feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.56,0:41:47.19,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,hora koko kara hajime you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.56,0:41:47.19,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Come on, let's start right here
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.90,0:41:52.73,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Just start in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.90,0:41:52.73,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Just start in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.74,0:41:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.28,0:41:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.57,0:41:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.57,0:42:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji got hurt the last time he was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.45,0:42:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I thought maybe your detective skills weren't quite\Ngood enough, since you were letting people get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.55,0:42:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the last time you were in Osaka,\Nyou didn't visit or stop to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.05,0:42:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was beginning to worry that Heiji was\Nfollowing someone with no responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.39,0:42:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that time you came and visited the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.69,0:42:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you at least one time, so I guess it's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.73,0:42:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he really has a reason to respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.40,0:42:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are someone with real intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.95,0:42:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.70,0:42:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were able to find Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} by phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.37,0:42:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Notice I was lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.42,0:42:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all the while solve a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.71,0:42:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all solved so swiftly!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.46,0:42:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I regret what's happened to Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.72,0:43:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did manage to recover the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.26,0:43:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.22,0:43:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you got bullied by the first year champion which\Nleft you crying and didn't care if the photograph was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.19,0:43:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have to worry at all now about leaving\NHeiji and Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} with you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.69,0:43:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.32,0:43:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, why do you have so much luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.99,0:43:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.66,0:43:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kid didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.08,0:43:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was serious on the phone?
